Step 1: Database Setup — Vector Ready

Before anything fancy, get the foundation right.
Key parameters
ALTER SYSTEM SET VECTOR_MEMORY_SIZE = 1G SCOPE=SPFILE;
ALTER SYSTEM SET FILESYSTEMIO_OPTIONS = SETALL SCOPE=SPFILE;

SHUTDOWN IMMEDIATE;
STARTUP;

Why this matters:
•	VECTOR_MEMORY_SIZE → enables fast vector ops 
•	FILESYSTEMIO_OPTIONS=SETALL → optimized I/O for large data loads 

