Import the APEX app export, run the DDL scripts in order, start the Flask service, and the demo is live.

•	Login to APEX : Access APEX URL and open App Builder 
•	Initiate Import : Click Import → Import File 
•	Upload File : Select the app_export.sql* export file 
•	Review Configuration : Verify App Name / App ID (change if needed) 
•	Select Schema : Choose correct parsing schema (tables, functions) 
•	Install Application : Click Install Application 
•	Run & Validate : Launch app and test key features


